TODO: fix icons

To reuse this code for a different OpenApp package
==================================================

1. edit module.def:
  a. search/replace Joomla with new app name
  b. generate two fresh UUIDs (and stick them in the right spots)
  c. update shortname/title/description to make sense
2. edit action:
  a. change appid= line to match /usr/bin/openapp-X-passwd
  b. change getconfig class line to match classname in module.def
3. change debian/changelog:
  a. change package name, perhaps update date
4. change debian/control:
  a. replace 'joomla' and 'Joomla' with new app name
5. change debian/postinst:
  a. replace 'Joomla' with new app name
6. change debian/rules:
  a. replace 'Joomla' with new app name
7. Change icon (to be fixed and described). 
  
That should be all!
